title: 16 Questions I Have About Mary-Kate & Ashley's "You're Invited" Series As An Adult
text:
View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com “We love them all. Especially the homework parties!”— said no kid ever.
ID: 10475202 2. Why did Mary-Kate & Ashley’s friend bring all those hats to a sleepover party? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com Four of them to be exact.
ID: 10476481 3. And why did their other friend bring a framed picture of a dog? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com Although, same TBH.
ID: 10476505 4. WHY and HOW was this kid holding an 80-pound boombox to his ear?! View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com ID: 10476559 5. Who was the genius behind the lyrics of this bop ? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com Whipped cream pouring like waterfalls. Watch it for five consecutive minutes here .
ID: 10501287 6. Why did they make their friends clean their kitchen in the Christmas party video? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com Nothing says “fun” like mopping your friend’s floor when you’re 10 years old.
ID: 10498902 7. Who paid for Mary-Kate, Ashley, and their friends to fly all the way to Minnesota for the mall party episode? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com ID: 10492796 8. WHERE were these girls’ parents when they decided to just pick themselves up and go on a vacation to Hawaii? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com I wasn’t even allowed to ride my bike down the street by myself…
ID: 10492223 9. What were they trying to teach us with this series? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com And how were they sharing that itty bitty suitcase?
ID: 10499083 10. Why were they dressed better/classier at 10 years old than I’ll ever be in my lifetime? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com ID: 10499133 Just LOOK. When I was this age I was sporting gaucho pants and braces? No, nope, definitely did NOT strut around like that at that age. Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com ID: 10501450 11. Did anyone else find it really fucking weird that these professional ballerinas let young children do their makeup and massage them? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com Just me? Okay.
ID: 10499206 12. Why was this drag of an episode even made? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via amazon.com This one was the WORST. Boring plot, unmemorable songs, *yawn.*
ID: 10499272 13. Why was this scene where they talk about their crushes so fucking cringeworthy? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com If you want to feel super uncomfortable for a good minute, scroll to 8:43 on the video here .
ID: 10499415 14. And what possessed them to keep making these You’re Invited videos? View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com They’re 13 here, damn it. Isn’t this getting lame?
ID: 10499771 15. I can’t even bring myself to come up with a question for this. Just WOW. Oy vey, wow. View this image ›
Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com ID: 10499832 16. And why was the You’re Invited theme song just so fucking catchy? Video available at: https://youtube.com/watch?v=yNe7VZcFLAo . Dualstar Video / Via youtube.com ID: 10499856
